title: Amazing Star Cast
review: A hidden good message is given in this movie. It has a basic story but the acting of all the star cast is so good that makes it an amazing film.

title: Perfect cinematography and direction
review: Not all the movies come with the perfect cinematography and direction but this movie has awesome concept and cinematography.

title: Interesting script
review: This movie is more than an average one, I like the theme and storyline. You would see so many heart felt emotions and an interesting script.
